{"tid":1175330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭 從來都係一個人嘅事","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T16:21:32.000Z","uid":59218,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2395d69b2d3a5c5952bab24f1f26ecd9c43d0ccb","tid":1175330,"uid":59218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNSo6UC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNSo6UC.png&h=e887e991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好鐘意V煞嘅電影<br />\n國家入面嘅每一個人都受住一個戴住奇怪面具嘅人嘅影響<br />\n面對極權<br />\n佢地心入面冇太多嘅爭扎<br />\n佢地選擇戴上面具<br />\n捨棄自己喺社會上嘅身份<br />\n今夜 戴上面具嘅佢地 每一個人都係平等<br />\n每一個都代表緊自己嘅意志<br />\n既然選擇咗 就要承擔<br />\n所以唔係因為其他人點做 所以我地點做<br />\n<br />\n抗爭 從來都係一個人嘅事<br />\n<br />\n所以 請諗清楚你6月9號點解會出現<br />\n<br />\n抗爭 即使最後只剩一個人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QXgHB6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QXgHB6.png&h=198391d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"682fc74a693c87db346ced0abbd6db2339d53933","tid":1175330,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b4b07aa3ee4af53e305489815c369daf8ddc47","tid":1175330,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682fc74a693c87db346ced0abbd6db2339d53933","tid":1175330,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"你理得人啫 多事"},{"pid":"3924bc96e4a6e6d072c409461d299facd0c3d5c0","tid":1175330,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"385569bdd4a910509d9cb1ea6dc25854e07a921b","tid":1175330,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf5792ca0abf20fc6f78e579a4a4bc549f4e0066","tid":1175330,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy